items.title: So Now the Left Is Against Government Extortion to Suppress Speech?
items.description: Congratulations, Democrats. You’re now living in the world you created.

items.title: Of Course the FCC Is Abusing Its Power over Broadcasting
items.description: It has done so before, and so long as it retains its power, it will do it again.

items.title: The Government Shouldn’t Police Jimmy Kimmel’s Lies
items.description: ABC and its affiliates may have pulled the trigger, but they did so with FCC guns pointed at their own heads if they did not.

items.title: A Visit to the University of Texas’s Art Museum in Austin
items.description: A nice place, but someone should explain what ‘extraction’ means to the wealth of the nation and people’s paychecks.

items.title: Charlie Kirk’s Horrific Murder Is a Tragedy — and a Warning
items.description: If we are to remain the place the Founders hoped we would be, then we cannot ever treat such events as acceptable or deserved.
